item.title: Japan Airport Runway Shut After US Cargo Plane Makes Emergency Landing
item.description: One of the two runways at Japan's Narita Airport was closed on Tuesday after an American cargo plane made an emergency landing due to an issue with its hydraulic system, officials said.
